      "instruction": "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees. Coat 6 cups of a muffin tin with cooking spray or line with paper liners."
    },
    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Crack the eggs into a large bowl. Use a Braun MultiQuick 7 Hand Blender or a whisk to blend the eggs until smooth, this will take less than a minute."
    },
    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Add the spinach, bacon and cheese to the egg mixture and stir to combine."
    },
    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Divide the egg mixture evenly among the muffin cups."
    },
    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Bake for 15-18 minutes or until eggs are set."
    },
